Software Installations.
-

1. Download and Install the NodeJS.

    Website : https://nodejs.org/en/download/
    file name : node-v6.10.3-x64.msi


2. Download and Install the Git

    website : https://git-scm.com/download/win
    file name : Git-2.13.0-64-bit.exe


3. Download and Install the WebStrom IDE.
    website :
https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/download/download-thanks.html?platform=windows

    file name : Webstrom-2017.1.3.exe


4. Create the Account with the GitHub.
    website : https://github.com/join


5. Checkout the Code from the GitHub
URL : https://github.com/ajsnaresh/AJS_Classes.git


6. Install the "bower" plugin
    - we can install bower by using nodejs commands.
        >npm install -g bower

7. Download and Install the mongoDB.
    website : https://www.mongodb.com/download-center#community
    file name : mongodb-win32-x86_64-2008plus-ssl-3.4.4-signed.msi

8. Download and Install  the "Postman"
    - Postman is the Software used to test the API Calls

    website : https://www.getpostman.com/

    file name : Postman-win64-4.10.7-Setup.exe